OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA spell of persistent rain
OL,6,Fspreads across the region during the
OL,7,Fmorning, followed by sunny spells and
OL,8,Fscattered showers in the afternoon.
OL,9,FThese could prove locally heavy,
OL,10,Fperhaps with the odd rumble of
OL,11,Fthunder. Turning increasingly windy
OL,12,Fthrough the day.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FFurther showers or longer
OL,15,Fspells of rain likely into the evening
OL,16,Fand overnight, some clear spells
OL,17,Flikely across the east of the region.
OL,18,FRemaining rather breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
